<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_212" id="106r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_212_r1l2">VVılhelm <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Seckkendorff von Dürnbuch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l3">vogt cʒu vvinſbach / </ab>
</div>
