<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_212_r1l4"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> wılhelm / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Gorgen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l5">Swaben vvegen / vvie der <expan>eıne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſchedlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>man<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd cʒu Berch - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l6">tolcʒdorff in fenknüſʒ <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſull etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l7">Vnd laſſen ewr Erberkeit wiſſen / daʒ vvir <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Gorgen Swaben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan></del> fur vns beſant vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> cʒu rede geſecʒt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l9">vnd der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / vvie das er einen gefangen het / der ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l10">ſein diener geweſt 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd hab auch </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_212_line_1576674711153_11098">der </ab></add> etwas vvider Jn getan 
<del rend="strikethrough">gehabt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_212_line_1576674708133_11093">het </ab></add> / den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l12">hab er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_212_line_1576674713838_11103">auch </ab></add> wider ledig gelaſſen / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>aſſumpc<ex>ionis</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_212" id="106r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhelm <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Seckkendorff von Dürnbuch, vogt czu
                        Winsbach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Wilhelm, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Gorgen Swaben wegen, wie der
                                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>schedliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>man<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> und czu Berchtolczdorff in fenknüsz
                                <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sull etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und lassen ewr erberkeit
                        wissen, daz wir <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Gorgen Swaben,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, fur uns besant und
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> czu rede geseczt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und der hat uns
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, wie das er einen gefangen het, der
                        sey sein diener gewest, <add>der</add> etwas wider in getan <add>het</add>,
                        den hab er <add>auch</add> wider ledig gelassen,
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>assumpc<ex>ionis.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
